{"id":"aa3c3d63e858fc110341ad61730f8572185423242bfb1ee1310a328f03f61e15","item_id":"cc42e10d94:0","text":"RenderMan 完整支持典型的 camera simulation（相机模拟），包括 PRMan 一直支持的两种标准 projection（投影）：perspective（透视）和 orthographic（正交），以及"}
{"id":"1ba941d3501ce6db76d6ee6d3a9376c41133b979ef3cb82e48d3c6dcbaef6eb5","item_id":"cc42e10d94:1","text":"motion blur（运动模糊）"}
{"id":"6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0","item_id":"cc42e10d94:2","text":"和"}
{"id":"e0181b1d7fdc69199d708d9ea71b7dd75bd04ade5d09afc74350b2970bdf50ec","item_id":"cc42e10d94:3","text":"camera effects（相机效果）"}
{"id":"14b5230a503337045fda833709c7d115e4a2222dc90c679f56da0f69b80add4c","item_id":"cc42e10d94:4","text":"等功能，例如 Depth of Field（景深）和 Bokeh（焦外散景）。"}
{"id":"3a42dcdfd1fb711a1a917aa79e5ab6e29b9360e54eae279419a57445192d3fe2","item_id":"cc42e10d94:5","text":"这些功能通过 projection plugins（投影插件）支持，使光线能够穿过以视点为中心的任意表面进行 tracing（追踪），这些表面还可能是弯曲的。发行包也包含 built-in projections（内置投影）："}
{"id":"0f58b78bc54e0c3e55568ec522fb67be295f3bf726a0d53cef872b7a4272196e","item_id":"cc42e10d94:6","text":"sphere"}
{"id":"c871dc1dcab70d1af97e8dd077b730d56f6f603c06173a0df57259a7139e28c3","item_id":"cc42e10d94:7","text":"torus"}
{"id":"921178a491aeb0a5fb466ad9aa254afd19c44270452270b6b738b8e0360d4700","item_id":"cc42e10d94:8","text":"，以及"}
{"id":"05fa0965c7c35c471dd1e8474b76870be2ec1ce535c2b169ab4f3554ab17e436","item_id":"cc42e10d94:9","text":"cylinder"}
{"id":"10649aecbe42f0beb69da961242dd4f97b399fba2a64df8de29a421b679613b8","item_id":"cc42e10d94:10","text":"，它们兼容 raytrace hider 的所有模式。"}
{"id":"d8fdaddac09347f519f8255bcfa146273f7e61ad28f44c53264ae335d71bc2a3","item_id":"cc42e10d94:11","text":"PxrCamera"}
